@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "_Layout";
}

<div class="container mt-5 text-light">
    <h1 class="text-warning fw-bold">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p class="mt-3">
        This Privacy Policy explains how the Business School platform collects, uses, and protects your personal information.
        We are committed to ensuring that your privacy is safeguarded and that your data is handled responsibly.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-warning mt-4">Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>
        We may collect personal details such as your name, email address, and academic information when you register or interact with the platform.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-warning mt-4">How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>
        The information collected is used to provide access to academic services, manage club registrations, and improve the overall user experience.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-warning mt-4">Data Protection</h3>
    <p>
        We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-warning mt-4">User Rights</h3>
    <p>
        You have the right to access, update, or request the deletion of your personal information. Please contact the administration for any privacy-related requests.
    </p>

 
</div>
